<br>
And even better than that, they added it to the loot table on griffins and griffons a few patches back.  <br>
<br>
Assuming you're making Royal tempers, the essence of sunlight will more likely be your holdup (it TLC's around lvl 50, and sand giants are usually only up in limited supply).  You can hunt it off Chromodracs though in Skyfire if you get desperate (but that zone is something of a pain).<br>
<br>
- Syll<br>
